getReviewResource

Gets the ReviewResource instance associating with the review id. Returns null if the review id does not exist.

Parameters:
reviewId - the review id.
isClone - true if the ReviewResource contains the clone of the review element. false if it contains the review element of the document.
Returns:
the ReviewResource instance associating with the review id. Returns null if the review id does not exist.
